# Gantt Chart for Project Timeline

## Project Gantt Chart

### Phases
1. **Development**: Jan 1 - Mar 13, 2026 (71 days)
2. **IST Readiness/Handover**: Mar 16 - Mar 27, 2026 (12 days)
3. **Functional/Interface/UAT Readiness**: Mar 28 - Apr 24, 2026 (28 days)
4. **UAT**: Apr 27 - May 22, 2026 (26 days)
5. **PROD Readiness**: May 23 - May 29, 2026 (7 days)
6. **Data Migration & Deployment**: May 30 - May 31, 2026 (2 days)

### Milestones
- Development complete by Mar 13, 2026.
- IST Readiness by Mar 27, 2026.
- UAT completion by May 22, 2026.

### Progress Tracking
- Track the percentage completion of each phase and visualize it on the Gantt chart.

## Timeline Details
- The chart visually represents the start and end date of each phase with progress color-coded to show current status of tasks.

## Conclusion
- The Gantt chart serves as a project management tool to track phases and deadlines in the project timeline.